  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Overview:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A survival horror game inspired by the great PS1 era classics. A blend of third person action, exploration, with light puzzle solving elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/80584970ec60767c7f6d8d5667c9b46f.poster.avif?t=1743381648\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/80584970ec60767c7f6d8d5667c9b46f.webm?t=1743381648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/80584970ec60767c7f6d8d5667c9b46f.mp4?t=1743381648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive the trauma</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something has transformed Lake Forest Academy. Its classrooms tell a story of terror and mystery. Its monsters a reflection of people's nightmares. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/55cb4e702662eba671a2e053faeb176f.poster.avif?t=1743381648\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/55cb4e702662eba671a2e053faeb176f.webm?t=1743381648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/55cb4e702662eba671a2e053faeb176f.mp4?t=1743381648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat the horrors</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Outsmart depraved creatures. Find a variety of weapons and items to help you venture deeper into the darkness.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/beaf81e5994df0d31f77939710184dfb.poster.avif?t=1743381648\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/beaf81e5994df0d31f77939710184dfb.webm?t=1743381648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/beaf81e5994df0d31f77939710184dfb.mp4?t=1743381648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endure deadly traps</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll be put in dangerous situations. Think hard and you may endure. Something doesn't want you here.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/882e09533aa79575ed0adfc5655c6e70.poster.avif?t=1743381648\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/882e09533aa79575ed0adfc5655c6e70.webm?t=1743381648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/882e09533aa79575ed0adfc5655c6e70.mp4?t=1743381648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unravel dark history</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The pieces were in front of everyone the whole time. Someone worked hard to hide the truth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/2dca7c00e1617ceee24cf69191af1b75.poster.avif?t=1743381648\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/2dca7c00e1617ceee24cf69191af1b75.webm?t=1743381648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/2dca7c00e1617ceee24cf69191af1b75.mp4?t=1743381648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You'll soon learn that Amy didn't die here. Something Took Her, but why...?</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features boss encounters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple weapons with unique characteristics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple environments to explore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat techniques that spice up the genre</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secret areas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2+ Hour runtime</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-crafted cutscenes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
