d.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/2dca7c00e1617ceee24cf69191af1b75.poster.avif?t=1743381648\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/2dca7c00e1617ceee24cf69191af1b75.webm?t=1743381648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445380/extras/2dca7c00e1617ceee24cf69191af1b75.mp4?t=1743381648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You'll soon learn that Amy didn't die here. Something Took Her, but why...?</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features boss encounters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple weapons with unique characteristics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple environments to explore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat techniques that spice up the genre</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secret areas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2+ Hour runtime</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-crafted cutscenes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
